<span class="yt-core-attributed-string--inline-block-mod" style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px;"><img alt="" class="ytCoreImageHost yt-core-attributed-string__image-element yt-core-attributed-string__image-element--image-alignment-vertical-center ytCoreImageContentModeScaleToFill ytCoreImageLoaded" style="height: 16px; width: 16px;" src="./requirements_files/emoji_u1f4cc.png"></span>Para garantir o certificado,  obrigatrio assistir  masterclass (aula 0) e s aulas 1, 2, 3 e 4 diretamente na plataforma.
<span class="yt-core-attributed-string--inline-block-mod" style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px;"><img alt="" class="ytCoreImageHost yt-core-attributed-string__image-element yt-core-attributed-string__image-element--image-alignment-vertical-center ytCoreImageContentModeScaleToFill ytCoreImageLoaded" style="height: 16px; width: 16px;" src="./requirements_files/emoji_u1f4cc.png"></span>O formulrio de solicitao do certificado ser liberado no dia 02/02/2026, na live de encerramento s <span class="" dir="auto" style="font-weight: 400;"><a class="yt-core-attributed-string__link yt-core-attributed-string__link--call-to-action-color" tabindex="0" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JW-UkKitRJ4&amp;t=1110s" target="" force-new-state="true">18:30</a></span>h.
<span class="yt-core-attributed-string--inline-block-mod" style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px;"><img alt="" class="ytCoreImageHost yt-core-attributed-string__image-element yt-core-attributed-string__image-element--image-alignment-vertical-center ytCoreImageContentModeScaleToFill ytCoreImageLoaded" style="height: 16px; width: 16px;" src="./requirements_files/emoji_u1f4cc.png"></span>As lives e a masterclass (aula 0) no possuem palavras-chave. Ao longo da seleo, sero 4 palavras-chave no total.
<span class="yt-core-attributed-string--inline-block-mod" style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px;"><img alt="" class="ytCoreImageHost yt-core-attributed-string__image-element yt-core-attributed-string__image-element--image-alignment-vertical-center ytCoreImageContentModeScaleToFill ytCoreImageLoaded" style="height: 16px; width: 16px;" src="./requirements_files/emoji_u1f4cc.png"></span>O contedo da imerso ficar disponvel para os participantes at 02/02, s 23h59. <span class="yt-core-attributed-string--inline-block-mod" style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px;"><img alt="" class="ytCoreImageHost yt-core-attributed-string__image-element yt-core-attributed-string__image-element--image-alignment-vertical-center ytCoreImageContentModeScaleToFill ytCoreImageLoaded" style="height: 16px; width: 16px;" src="./requirements_files/emoji_u1f4cc.png"></span>Os materiais de apoio disponveis esto no rodap das aulas dentro da plataforma.

Eu pausei e fui aprender a usar direito as demais ferramentas, voltei e consegui chegar at o final . Mas, ainda acho que a aula foi boa pra aprender que I.A realmente  indispensvel pra quem ta comeando a aprender agora. Eu por exemplo, pedi pra I.A instalar o PIP no VSCode, instalar as bibliotecas, executar tudo. Pq pelos comandos, no dava certo. Usem e abusem das <span class="" dir="auto" style="font-weight: 400;"><a class="yt-core-attributed-string__link yt-core-attributed-string__link--call-to-action-color" tabindex="0" role="button" href="javascript:void(0);">I.As</a></span>  uma ferramenta que ta a pra isso mesm.</span></yt-attributed-string>

Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned 

volte ao VS Code e execute novamente o comando .venv\Scripts\Activate.
funcionou pra mim</span></yt-attributed-string>

Abaixo o que aconteceu e o que fiz. OBS: IA ajudou
 1 - Erro de permisso para ativar o python no VSC. Corrigi no Power Shell, com o comando Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser e depois sim/yes

2. Bibliotecas (pandas, streamlit e plotly ) no instaladas com o comando indicado (pip install -r requirements.txt) ,usei o comando pip install NOME DA BLIBLIOTECA --only-binary :all: 
Depois foi tranquilo.</span></yt-attributed-string>
